Experiment 2
--------------
Adding data augmentation to CNN to see how it helps solve overfitting. Training data accurracy is: 84.71% and
Test Data accurracy is : 60.56%. Yes, it is less overfitting, but there's another issue now.After augmentation:

Training accuracy dropped by about 15 percentage points.
That's expected because the training images are now harder—every epoch the model sees slightly different versions of the same images.
The test accuracy also dropped dramatically, from 77.46% to 60.56%. 
Possible problems: augumentation to aggressive, training for too few epochs